=\"fn\">v</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set.image\">''</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">{</a><span class=\"fn\">i</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">:</a> <span class=\"fn\">ι</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">|</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">v</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span></span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">}</a>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"**Alias** of `Submonoid.closure_image_isMulIndecomposable_baseOf`.\n\n---\n\nGiven a finite family of points `v` in a monoid `M`, together with a morphism into a\nlinearly-ordered monoid `f : M →* S`, the submonoid generated by those points of `v` which lie in\nthe \"half space\" where `f > 1` is generated by the subset of such points which are indecomposable\nwith respect to points in this half space. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Irreducible/Indecomposable.html#Submonoid.closure_image_one_lt_and_isMulIndecomposable","kind":"theorem","line":114,"name":"Submonoid.closure_image_one_lt_and_isMulIndecomposable","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Irreducible/Indecomposable.lean#L114-L116"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Irreducible/Indecomposable.html#AddSubmonoid.closure_image_isAddIndecomposable_baseOf\"><span class=\"name\">AddSubmonoid</span>.<span class=\"name\">closure_image_isAddIndecomposable_baseOf</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ι</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span clas